sically you get items that are turned in as quest items.  And I thing some of the items (have to research more) are used by multiple professions.  Just for example (not sure which items) one item can be used in conjunction for others to obtain a monk sash, or that item can be used with others for a Cleric helm.<br>
<br>
However, if we have enough people that want to do it, and are willing to commit a couple days in a row to do it, I will schedule and run the event.<br>
<br>
So, some feedback please <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
