<br>
I haven't completed any quests myself.  I have pulled from the second island (technically the third island) a couple of times.  However, seeing how you have done four quests, could you comment and give a run down of things based on your experience.  I would naturally research this further also, however, I want to see if at least there is a desire to go.<br>
